: 310, \"to\": 326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been 200 days since they are sitting here.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"200 days\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is painful to see this.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of them are citizens of this country.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"citizens\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"this country\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Farmers run the country.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Farmers\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing is possible without them, not even athletes-if they do not feed us, we will not be able to compete,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat continued, \\\"Many a time we are helpless and can not do anything.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Phogat\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We represent the country at such big levels, but we can not do anything for our family even when we see them sad.\\\"\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"such big levels\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"our family\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I urge the Government that they should listen.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Government\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They had admitted their mistake last time; they should fulfill the promises that they made.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their mistake\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the promises\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The country will not progress if people sit on the streets like this,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The country\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The protest which enters the 200th day today began on February 13, after authorities prevented their march to Delhi.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9999998114926889, \"rank\": 1.8850719423223123e-07, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The protest\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200th day\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"their march\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The farmers have raised the issue of Minimum Support Price (MSP) for all crops, a demand which has not yet been met by the Centre.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament\", \"score\": 0.7607185262690458, \"rank\": 0.31454639490988523, \"text\": \"MSP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_S